ida Sports Complex Ground|Greater Noida]] || 10 March 2017\n|- \n| 2 || 5/11 || '''[[Karim Janat]]''' || {{cr|WIN}} || [[Bharat Ratna Shri Atal Bihari Vajpayee Ekana Cricket Stadium|Lucknow]] || 16 November 2019\n|- \n| 3 || 5/13  || [[Samiullah Shinwari]] || {{cr|KEN}} || [[Sharjah Cricket Stadium|Sharjah]] || 24 November 2013\n|-\n| 4 || 5/27 || '''[[Rashid Khan (cricketer)|Rashid Khan]]''' || {{cr|IRE}} || [[Rajiv Gandhi International Cricket Stadium, Dehradun|Dehradun]] || 24 February 2019\n|-\n| 5 || 4/10 || '''[[Mohammad Nabi]]''' || {{cr|IRE}} || [[Dubai International Cricket Stadium|Dubai]] || 20 January 2017\n|-\n| colspan=6 | <small>Last updated: 25 November 2019</small><ref>{{cite web|title=Records / Afghanistan / Twenty20 Internationals / Best bowling figures in an innings|url=http://stats.espncricinfo.com/ci/engine/records/bowling/best_figures_innings.html?class=3;id=40;type=team|publisher=ESPNcricinfo|accessdate=22 August 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==== Most career wickets ====\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:60%;\"\n|-\n! Rank !! Wickets !! Player !! Matches !! [[Bowling analysis|BBI]]\n|-\n| 1 || 87 || '''[[Rashid Khan (cricketer)|Rashid Khan]]''' || 47 || 5/3\n|-\n| 2 || 69 || '''[[Mohammad Nabi]]''' || 77 || 4/10\n|-\n| 3 || 40 || [[Dawlat Zadran]] || 34 || 4/44\n|-\n| 4 || 37 || '''[[Shapoor Zadran]]''' || 36 || 3/40\n|-\n| 5 || 32 || [[Hamid Hassan]] || 22 || 4/22\n|-\n| colspan=5 | <small>Last updated: 25 November 2019</small><ref>{{cite web|title=Records / Afghanistan / Twenty20 Internationals / Most wickets|url=http://stats.espncricinfo.com/ci/engine/records/bowling/most_wickets_career.html?class=3;id=40;type=team|publisher=ESPNcricinfo|accessdate=23 August 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==== Best career economy rate ====\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:60%;\"\n|-\n! Rank !! [[Economy rate (cricket)|Economy rate]] !! Player !! Overs !! Runs\n|-\n| 1 || 6.01 || '''[[Rashid Khan (cricketer)|Rashid Khan]]''' || 175.0 || 1,052\n|-\n| 2 || 6.04 || ''