, 2018|accessdate=January 12, 2018}}</ref>\n| [[IHeartRadio Music Award for Female Artist of the Year|Female Artist of the Year]]\n| rowspan=\"4\" | Herself\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[2018 Billboard Music Awards|''Billboard'' Music Awards]]\n|[[Billboard Music Award for Top Female Artist|Top Female Artist]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[Billboard Music Award for Top Radio Songs Artist|Top Radio Songs Artist]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[29th GLAAD Media Awards|GLAAD Media Awards]]\n| [[GLAAD Media Award for Outstanding Music Artist|Outstanding Music Artist]]\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|[[2018 Teen Choice Awards|Teen Choice Awards]]\n|Choice Song: Female Artist\n|\"[[Bad at Love]]\"\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |[[2018 iHeartRadio Much Music Video Awards|iHeartRadio Much Music Video Awards]]\n|Video of the Year\n|\"Bad at Love\"\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|Best Pop Artist or Group\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Herself\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|Fan Fave Artist\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"30\" |2019\n| rowspan=\"4\" |[[Global Awards]]\n|Rising Star Award\n| rowspan=\"3\" |Herself\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|Best Female\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|Social Media Superstar\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|Best Song\n|\"[[Eastside (song)|Eastside]]\"\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |[[iHeartRadio Music Awards]]\n|Best Lyrics\n|\"[[Without Me (Halsey song)|Without Me]]\"\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|Best Cover Song\n|\"[[Lucid Dreams (Juice Wrld song)|Lucid Dreams]]\"\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|Female Artist of the Year\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Herself\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|Fangirls Award\n|{{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[iHeartRadio]] Titanium Award<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/cardi-b-post-malone-camila-cabello-iheartradio-titanium-award-816485/|title=Cardi B, Post Malone, Camila Cabello Receive iHeartRadio Titanium Award|first1=Althea|last1=Legaspi|date=April 2, 2019}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Winning songs \n|\"Bad at Love\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" {{won}}\n|-\n|\"[[Him & I]]\"\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[2019 Billboard Music Awards|''Billboard'' Music Awards]]\n|Top Female Artist\n|Herself\n|