op]]\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|[[MTV Video Music Award for Best Art Direction|Best Art Direction]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[MTV Video Music Award for Best Choreography|Best Choreography]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|Video for Good\n|rowspan=\"2\"| \"Nightmare\"\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|Best Power Anthem\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |[[American Music Awards of 2019|American Music Awards]]\n| [[American Music Award for Artist of the Year|Artist of the Year]]\n| Herself\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[American Music Award for Video of the Year|Favorite Music Video]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" | \"Without Me\"\n| {{nom}}\n|- \n| Favorite Pop/Rock Song\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2020\n| rowspan=\"4\" | [[2020 iHeartRadio Music Awards|iHeartRadio Music Awards]]\n| Female Artist of the Year\n| Herself\n| {{pending}}\n|-\n| Best Lyrics\n| \"Nightmare\"\n| {{pending}}\n|-\n| [[IHeartRadio Music Award for Best Music Video|Best Music Video]]\n| \"Boy with Luv\"\n| {{pending}}\n|-\n| Best Remix\n| \"Without Me\" (featuring [[Juice Wrld]])\n| {{pending}}\n|-\n|}\n\n==See also==\n\n{{Wikipedia books|Halsey}}\n\n* [[LGBT culture in New York City#Self-identifying LGBTQ New Yorkers|LGBTQ culture in New York City]]\n*[[List of people with bipolar disorder]]\n*[[List of artists who reached number one in the United States]]\n*[[List of artists who reached number one on the US dance chart|List of artists who reached number one on the U.S. dance chart]]\n*[[List of artists who reached number one on the Billboard Mainstream Top 40 chart|List of artists who reached number one on the ''Billboard'' Mainstream Top 40 chart]]\n\n== Notes ==\n{{notelist}}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{commons category|Halsey (singer)}}\n* {{Official website|http://iamhalsey.com}}\n\n{{Halsey}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Halsey}}\n[[Category:Halsey (singer)| ]]\n[[Category:1994 births]]\n[[Category:21st-century American singers]]\n[[Category:Activists from New Jersey]]\n[[Category:African-American female singers]]\n[[