lm-review-empty-hands-stephy-tang-actress-transformed-atmospheric|title=Review: Stephy Tang is an actress transformed in The Empty Hands|work=South China Morning Post|access-date=2018-06-22|language=en}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Chrissie Chau]]\n|''[[29+1]]''\n|Christy Lam\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.scmp.com/culture/film-tv/article/2093693/film-review-291-chrissie-chau-joyce-cheng-tale-women-turning-30|title=Film review: 29+1 \u2013 Kearen Pang\u2019s bittersweet tale of two women|work=South China Morning Post|access-date=2018-06-22|language=en}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" |'''[[List of Hong Kong films of 2018|2018]]<br><small>[[38th Hong Kong Film Awards|(38th)]]</small>'''\n| style=\"background:#FAEB86\" |[[Chloe Maayan]]\n| style=\"background:#FAEB86\" |''[[Three Husbands (2018 film)|Three Husbands]]''\n| style=\"background:#FAEB86\" |Ah Mui\n|\n| rowspan=\"5\" |<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hkfaa.com/winnerlist38.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190415071051/http://www.hkfaa.com/winnerlist38.html|url-status=dead|archive-date=2019-04-15|title=\u9999\u6e2f\u96fb\u5f71\u91d1\u50cf\u734e|website=\u9999\u6e2f\u96fb\u5f71\u91d1\u50cf\u734e|access-date=2019-02-12}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Charlene Choi]]\n|''[[The Lady Improper]]''\n| Siu Man\n|\n|-\n|[[Zhang Jingchu]]\n|''[[Project Gutenberg (film)|Project Gutenberg]]''\n|Yuen Man\n|\n|-\n|[[Jennifer Yu (actress)|Jennifer Yu]]\n|''Distinction''\n| Qian Siying\n|\n|-\n|[[Crisel Consunji]]\n|''[[Still Human]]''\n|Evelyn Santos\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" |'''[[List of Hong Kong films of 2019|2019]]<br><small>[[39th Hong Kong Film Awards|(39th)]]</small>'''\n|[[Sammi Cheng]]\n|''[[Fagara (film)|Fagara]]''\n| Acacia Ha\n|\n|-\n|[[Sammi Cheng]]\n|''[[Fatal Visit]]''\n| Ling\n|\n|-\n|[[Zhou Dongyu]]\n|''[[Better Days (film)|Better Days]]''\n| Chen Nian\n|\n|-\n|[[Cecilia Choi]]\n|''[[Beyond The Dream]]''\n| Yan / Yip Lam\n|\n|-\n|[[Stephy Tang]]\n|''[[My Prince Edward]]''\n| Fong\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n==Multiple wins and nominations==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-break}}\nThe following individuals received two or more Best Actress awards:\n{| class=\"wikitable\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align: center;\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"4\" background: #f6e39c;\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"55\"     | Wins\n! scope=\"col\" align=\"center\" | Actress\n! scope=\"col\" align=\"center\" | Years\n|-\n| rowspan=1 style=\"text-align:center\" | 5\n| [[Maggie Cheung]]\n| [[9th Hong Kong Film Awards|1990]], [[12th Hong Kong Film Awards|1993]], [[16th Hong Kong Film Awards|1997]], [[13th Hong Kong Film Awards|1998]], [[20th Hong Kong Film Awards|2001]] \n|-\n| rowspan=1 style=\"text-align:center\" | 3\n| [[Kara Wai]]\n| [[1st Hong Kong Film Awards|1982]], [[29th Hong Kong Film Awards|2010]], [[36th Hong Kong Film Awards|2017]]\n|-\n| rowspan=6 style=\"text-align:center\" | 2\n| [[Anita Yuen]]\n| [[13th Hong Kong Film Awards|1994]], [[14th Hong Kong Film Awards|1995]]\n|-\n| [[Cecilia Yip]]\n| [[3rd Hong Kong Film Awards|1984]], [[11th Hong Kong Film Awards|1992]]\n|-\n| [[Josephine Siao]]\n| [[7th Hong Kong Film Awards|1988]], [[15th Hong Kong Film Awards|1996]]\n|-\n|[[Siqin Gaowa]]\n| [[4th Hong Kong Film Awards|1985]], [[27th Hong Kong Film Awards|2008]]\n|-\n|[[Sylvia Chang]]\n| [[6th Hong Kong Film Awards|1987]], [[21st Hong Kong Film Awards|2002]]\n|-\n|[[Ziyi Zhang]]\n| [[24th Hong Kong Film Awards|2005]], [[33rd Hong Kong Film Awards|2014]]\n|}\n\n{{col-break}}\n\nThe following individuals received five or more Best Actress nominations:\n{| class=\"wikitable\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align: center;\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"4\" background: #f6e39c;\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"55\"     | Nominations\n! scope=\"col\" align=\"center\" | Actress\n|-\n| rowspan=1 style=\"text-align:center\" | 10\n| [[Sylvia Chang]]\n|-\n| rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center\" | 9\n| [[Maggie Cheung]]\n|-\n| [[Sammi Cheng]]\n|-\n|rowspan=4 style=\"text-align:center\" | 6\n| [[Carina Lau]]\n|-\n| [[Karena Lam]]\n|-\n| [[Zhou Xun]]\n|-\