omag.co.uk/art/asian-film/video/773/miriam-yeung-and-shawn-yue-enjoy-love-in-the-buff |title=Miriam Yeung and Shawn Yue Enjoy Love In The Buff |last=West |first=David |date=8 March 2012 |website=[[Neo (magazine)|Neo Magazine]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215031609/http://www.neomag.co.uk/art/asian-film/video/773/miriam-yeung-and-shawn-yue-enjoy-love-in-the-buff |archive-date=15 February 2017 |url-status=dead|access-date=12 February 2017 |df= }}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"5\" | <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hkfaa.com/winnerlist32.html |title=32nd Hong Kong Film Awards |last= |first= |date= |website= |publisher=[[Hong Kong Film Awards]] |language=Chinese |access-date=2 February 2017 |url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160922204644/http://www.hkfaa.com/winnerlist32.html |archivedate=22 September 2016 |df= }}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Sammi Cheng]]\n|''[[Romancing in Thin Air]]''\n|Sue\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2770947/romancing-in-thin-air-johnnie-to-masterpiece/ |title='Romancing in Thin Air': Get to Know Johnnie To's Masterpiece |last=Marsh |first=Calum |date=27 July 2013 |website= |publisher=[[MTV]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215024636/http://www.mtv.com/news/2770947/romancing-in-thin-air-johnnie-to-masterpiece/ |archive-date=15 February 2017 |url-status=live|access-date=14 February 2017 |df= }}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Elanne Kong]]\n|''[[Love Lifting]]''\n|Li Li\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.scmp.com/article/995526/love-lifting |title=Love Lifting |last= |first= |date=15 March 2012 |newspaper=[[South China Morning Post]] |access-date=14 February 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215021756/http://www.scmp.com/article/995526/love-lifting |archive-date=15 February 2017 |url-status=live|work= |via= |df= }}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Zhou Xun]]\n|{{sort|Great Magician|''[[The Great Magician]]''}}\n|Liu Yin\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/great-magician-filmart-review-302829 |title=Th